Enable loose mode: if the announced X-PAD length of a DAB+ service does not match the available X-PAD length the X-PAD is discarded. Revert "Use unique_ptr for dabProcessor"

Because I don't understand the interaction between a QObject and
a unique_ptr enough. Both seem to take ownership of the dabProcessor,
and when the unique_ptr wants to delete it, we get a double free.

This reverts commit dc994bbfa4f17c5701256f3ce4461ab48774c19f.
